{"title":"Men","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Oak Shampoo For Men 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA modern approach to the world of men – primal and earthy components create a shampoo with a light, modern and delicate nature! A natural shampoo for everyday use. The shampoo with a fine lather and minimal composition contains a powerful oak root extract that soothes irritated scalp and stimulates hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 – 25 degrees. Protect from direct sunlight during storage. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Methyl Oleoyl Taurate, Lauryl Glucoside, Coco-Glucoside, Parfum, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Citric Acid, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Panthenol, Pentylene Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,88%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927684231495,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-oak-shampoo-for-men-250ml-302851.png?v=1739897400"},{"product_id":"solid-oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Solid Oak Shampoo For Men 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003ch6\u003e\n\u003cimg height=\"100\" width=\"93\" alt=\"pure beauty global awars 2022 winner\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/908145_pbga_winner_2022-280x300.png\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12056\"\u003e \u003cimg height=\"100\" width=\"87\" alt=\"pure beauty global awars 2022 highly commended\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/908142_pbga_highly_commended_2022-261x300.png\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12051\"\u003e\n\u003c\/h6\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA modern approach to the world of men – primal and earthy components create a shampoo with a light, modern and delicate nature! The richly-foaming, deep-cleaning solid shampoo ensures clean and healthy hair. The shampoo with a rich foam and minimal composition contains powerful oak root extract and cocoa butter, which together soothe irritated scalp and stimulate hair growth. The dynamic formula deep-cleans and facilitates styling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak extract\u003c\/span\u003e has natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 – 25 degrees. Protect from direct sunlight during storage. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Quercus Robur (Oak) Extract, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96,6%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927694061895,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-solid-oak-shampoo-for-men-58g-324609.png?v=1739897402"},{"product_id":"oak-shower-gel-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Oak Shower Gel For Men 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour healthy, clean, moisturized skin! The sulphate-free shower gel is designed specifically for men and contains aloe, which moistens and calms the skin, and the powerful oak root extract, which pampers and caresses irritated skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Body\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe extract \u003c\/span\u003epromotes wound healing, moisturizes, refreshes, is anti-inflammatory, soothes, softens irritation and protects the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak root extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements. Rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Quercus Robur (Oak) Root Extract, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Isostearamide MIPA, Panthenol, Parfum, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 91,64%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927700713799,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-oak-shower-gel-for-men-250ml-478014.png?v=1739897400"},{"product_id":"hej-sensitive-24h-cream-50ml","title":"HEJ Organic Organic Sensitive 24h Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSimply a delicate all-rounder that provides intensive moisture and ensures radiant skin. Rich and quickly absorbed texture ensures that the skin feels pleasant, no matter what time of day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePromotes the balance of your skin barrier and deeply hydrates\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eQuickly absorbed texture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural power active ingredient complex made from hemp oil, oat and chamomile extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Especially for sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAllergen-reduced perfume oil, 100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHemp Oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains important Omega-6 fatty acids, promotes cell regeneration and protects the skin without feeling greasy.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOat Extract\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-inflammatory and calming effect and is particularly suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eChamomile Flower Water\u003c\/span\u003e has soothing and antibacterial characteristics and provides intensive hydration to the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to your face morning and evening after cleansing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cetearyl Alcohol, Distarch Phosphate, Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil*, Hydrogenated Rapeseed Oil, Candelilla Cera, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract*, Hypericum Perforatum Extract*, Avena Sativa Kernel Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Alcohol, Tocopherol, Citric Acid, Parfum** *ingredients from certified organic agriculture, **natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49509036327239,"sku":"","price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-organic-sensitive-24h-face-cream-50ml-375353.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser","title":"MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Moisturiser 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis lightweight moisturiser improves the hydration of sensitive, easily irritated, redness-prone skin. Biotechnologically obtained molecules of seaweed work to balance the skin's microbiome and reinforce its natural protection against external stressors. Minimises the appearance of redness and burning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin daily. Use in combination with MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Night Cream for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Glycerin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium PCA, Coco- Caprylate, Isoamyl Laurate, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Aqua, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Octyldodecanol, Xanthan Gum, Cellulose, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858966782279,"sku":"","price":39.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-643317.jpg?v=1739897262"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-hydra-recharge-cream-50ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS Hydra Recharge Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eSOS Hydra Recharge Cream, intense moisture-locking cream infused with age-defying antioxidants of peony, linseed and hyaluronic acid. Hydrates, replenishes and calms dehydrated and stressed skin to restore youthful radiance. Acting as a protective layer against environmental damage, this soft-textured cream reduces the look of fine lines, and promotes optimal hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin every morning and evening or whenever your skin feels thirsty or stressed. For the best results, use in combination with SOS Hydra Repair Intensive Serum.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Glyceryl Stearate, Behenyl Alcohol, Isoamyl Laurate, Rosa Damascena (Rose) Flower Water, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Aroma, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Cellulose, Sodium anisate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Lactic Acid, Glycine Soja Sterols, Linum Usitatissimum (Flax) Seed Extract, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Extract, Xanthan Gum, Paeonia Lactiflora (Peony) Root Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Tocopherol, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol, Geraniol, Benzyl Salicylate, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49859035300167,"sku":null,"price":37.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-hydra-recharge-cream-50ml-242361.jpg?v=1739897239"},{"product_id":"madara-anti-fatigue-eye-rescue-cream-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Anti-Fatigue Eye Rescue Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe unique multi-layered texture firms and smooths away signs of fatigue. Age-defying Smart Antioxidant complex of Lichen, Moss, Fern and Alchemilla hydrates and corrects fine lines and wrinkles.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSkin-dynamising natural aescin boosts circulation and strengthens capillaries to depuff and reduce dark circles and brighten up the eye area.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply 4 small drops around the eye and pat into the skin. Use morning and night.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Isoamyl Laurate, Arachidyl Alcohol, Behenyl Alcohol, Dipalmitoyl hydroxyproline, Sodium levulinate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Arachidyl Glucoside, Caffeine, Propanediol, Aroma, Glyceryl Caprylate, Sodium anisate, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Mica (CI 77019), Xanthan Gum, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Alchemilla Vulgaris (Lady's Mantle) Extract, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Coco-glucoside, Sodium PCA, Xylitylglucoside, Anhydroxylitol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Polypodium Vulgare (Fern) Rhizome Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Tocopherol, Xylitol, Potassium Hydroxide, Cetraria Islandica (Lichen) Thallus Extract, Citric acid, Sphagnum Magellanicum (Moss) Extract, Vanillin, Escin, Benzyl Salicylate, Limonene, Citral, Linalool, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887831753031,"sku":null,"price":32.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-anti-fatigue-eye-rescue-cream-15ml-826053.jpg?v=1739897249"},{"product_id":"madara-sebum-control-clear-skin-wash-140ml","title":"MÁDARA Sebum Control Clear Skin Wash 140ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFree from harsh surfactants, this plant-based cleanser purifies acne-prone skin, helping to minimize the appearance of blackheads and blemishes. Fermented polyaccharides help to regulate sebum and balance the microbiome for a healthy-looking skin. Juniper stem cells and extracts of lichen and mate deliver soothing and antioxidant benefits. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin, rinse off. Follow with a moisturiser. Use in combination with other ACNE formulas for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-glucoside, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Xanthan Gum, Propanediol, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Lactic Acid, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Aroma, Acacia Senegal Gum, Alcohol, Sodium anisate, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Rhamnose, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract, Glucose, Glucuronic Acid, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887907905863,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sebum-control-clear-skin-wash-140ml-429167.jpg?v=1739897250"},{"product_id":"madara-intense-blemish-pore-treatment-20ml","title":"MÁDARA Intense Blemish \u0026 Pore Serum 20ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eEnriched with soothing and keratolytic actives, this intensive cream helps to keep your complexion pure and balanced. Improves the condition and appearance of oily, clogged and problem-prone skin. Good for teenagers and adults.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a thin layer on blemish-prone areas morning and\/or night. Follow with a moisturiser. Use as a 6 week course or regularly. For best results, use in combination with the rest of ACNE solutions.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Alcohol, Glycerin, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil, Cannabis Sativa (Hemp) Seed Oil, Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Leaf Oil, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Salicylic Acid, Betaine, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Sodium PCA, Tocopherol, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Zinc PCA, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Cellulose, Potassium Hydroxide, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract, Maltodextrin, CI 75815 (Chlorophyllin Copper Complex), Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887983337799,"sku":null,"price":18.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-intense-blemish-pore-serum-20ml-5911846.jpg?v=1770966612"},{"product_id":"madara-spot-roll-on-8ml","title":"MÁDARA Spot Roll-On 8ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis powerful, concentrated solution attacks blemishes on contact. Juniper Stem Cells and Salicylic Acid instantly get spots under control. Invisible to the skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply directly to blemishes. Reapply after 2 hours if necessary. For external use only. Keep out of the eye and lip area. For best results, use in combination with the rest of ACNE solutions.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Alcohol, Aqua, Salicylic Acid, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Potassium Hydroxide, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49888025837895,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-spot-roll-on-8ml-692861.jpg?v=1739897262"},{"product_id":"madara-hydra-derm-balancing-fluid-40ml","title":"MÁDARA Hydra-Derm Balancing Fluid 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis light-weight face moisturiser intensely hydrates and balances, ensuring lasting comfort and helping to improve the condition of problem-prone skin. Helps to tighten pores and minimise the appearance of breakouts.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFormulated with moisturising hyaluronic acid and fermented polysaccharides that regulate the microbiome for a clear and healthy-looking complexion. Juniper stem sells and extracts of lichen and mate tea deliver strong soothing and antioxidant benefits. Targets both teenage and adult acne.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin every morning and night. Use in combination with other ACNE formulas for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Glycerin, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cellulose, Sodium PCA, Isoamyl Laurate, Zinc PCA, Aroma, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Propanediol, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Alcohol, Xanthan Gum, Ilex Paraguariensis (Mate) Leaf Extract, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Potassium Hydroxide, Sodium phytate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Cetraria Islandica (Iceland Moss) Extract, Usnea Barbata (Lichen) Extract, Rhamnose, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Callus Culture Extract, CI 77007 (Ultramarines), Glucose, Glucuronic Acid, Silica, Kaolin, Maltodextrin, CI 75815 (Chlorophyllin Copper Complex), Linalool, Citral, Limonene, Citronellol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49888070107463,"sku":"","price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-hydra-derm-balancing-fluid-40ml-855043.jpg?v=1739897240"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe multitasking Naïf Nurturing Day Cream hydrates and protects face, neck and décolleté during the day from the harmful effects of UV radiation. Al this thanks to the added tomato extract. To support the natural skin process, the day cream contains natural oils, such as avocado and almond oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe day cream is quickly absorbed and you don't need much of it. That's why you'll be able to use the bioplastic tube's content even longer. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the Nurturing Day Cream evenly (you don't need much) to a cleansed face, neck and décolleté.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe natural SPF6 from tomato extract provides for protection against harmful UV rays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed Seed) Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Solanum Lycopersicum (Tomato Fruit\/Leaf\/Stem) Extract, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary Leaf) Extract, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915540205895,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-773702.png?v=1739897170"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNaïf Nurturing Night Cream contributes to a good night's sleep. The regenerating night cream soothes the skin and supports the natural skin process. Includes almond oil, shea butter and macadamia extract for ultimate hydration and moisture retention. No more dry spots!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream absorbs quickly, doesn't stick and doesn't make the skin feel tight. So you don't have to worry when resting your head on your pillow. The night cream is made without mineral oils, microplastics and silicones.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Naïf regenerating night cream is for every skin type. So also for the most sensitive skin. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eA night cream is best applied if you apply a good, thick amount. Do this on clean, cleansed skin. And don't forget to apply it to the neck and décolleté. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/ Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Methylpropanediol, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Sucrose Stearate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus, (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915767255367,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml-623217.png?v=1739897168"},{"product_id":"naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml","title":"NAIF Circular Face Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Circular Face Scrub cleanses your skin and removes dead skin cells, stimulating cell renewal. Result: radiant skin. The face scrub also contains natural oils, such as macadamia, avocado and sweet almond oil. These ingredients condition your skin and keep your skin soft and supple, without making your face feel tight, after exfoliating. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are 100% vegan, made with a gentle fragrance and are dermatologically tested, free from the 26 most common allergens. Mild for the skin, due to the fine grain, which also allows you to use the scrub several times a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eScrub your face once or twice a week for beautiful, healthy skin. Slightly moisten your face and apply the pea-sized scrub to the inside of your hand. Using your fingers, massage the scrub onto your face for at least 30 seconds using circular motions. Rinse with lukewarm water. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Calcium Carbonate, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Methylpropanediol, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Linum Usitatissimum Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Parfum, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Phenylpropanol, Bisabolol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915785441607,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-circular-face-scrub-50ml-570470.png?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-face-wash-100ml","title":"NAIF Cleansing Face Wash 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gel transforms into a milky formula on contact with water. The advantage of this gel-to-milk formula is that it cleanses the skin without drying it out. Therefore, this face cleanser is suitable for all skin types, even for very oily or sensitive skin and the thinner skin around the eyes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBecause the facial cleanser contains natural oils, the skin's PH level remains undisturbed and the skin feels moisturized and supple afterward.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested, and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMoisten the face with lukewarm water. Apply a fingertip-sized amount of gel to a (washable) cotton pad or in the palm of your hand and massage the gel all over your face. The gel will now have a milky texture and slowly foams. After cleansing, rinse with lukewarm water, pat skin dry and apply a nourishing day or night cream. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHelianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Glycerin, Aqua\/Water, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Sucrose Palmitate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Caprylyl Glycol, Tocopherol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915798712647,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cleansing-face-wash-100ml-376187.png?v=1739897186"},{"product_id":"nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-for-men-4-5g","title":"NURME Protective Mint Lip Balm for Men 4,5g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith cocoa butter and vitamin E. Lip balm for men protects against cold, wind and sun. Softens lips and prevents chapping. The lip balm has a pleasantly refreshing mint scent.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to lips.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCera Alba (Beeswax), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Mentha Viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Limonene*, Linalool*. * Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915925885255,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-for-men-45g-899941.webp?v=1739897164"},{"product_id":"madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA PEEL Brightening AHA Peel mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eGive your skin an instant radiance boost with this active AHA peeling mask. Formulated with nature’s superdose of active acids, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: Removes the dead cells to uncover smoother, more radiant skin surface, exfoliates to stimulate cell turnover and regeneration, brightens the complexion and diminishes appearance of age-spots and fine lines, helps to unclog pores and improves the absorption and effect of other cosmetic products. Especially beneficial for dull, tired skin with signs of aging, lines, wrinkles, age-spots, lack of glow, clogged pores and acne.\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e ​Apply to clean skin, leave on for 3–10 minutes. Rinse off thoroughly, follow with a toner and moisturiser of your choice.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Lactic Acid, Glycerin, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Water, Galactoarabinan, Potassium Hydroxide, Microcrystalline Cellulose, Glucomannan, Mica (CI 77019), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Aroma, Cellulose gum, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Fruit Extract, Sambucus Nigra (Elder) Flower Extract, Ethyl Lauroyl Arginate HCl, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916404298055,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-peel-brightening-aha-peel-mask-60ml-412418.jpg?v=1739897193"},{"product_id":"madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA DETOX Ultra Purifying MUD mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eClarify, rejuvenate and recharge the skin with this deep-purifying detox mask. Formulated with Nordic forest lake mud, this mask ensures multiple skincare benefits: it purifies the complexion, tightens pores and conditions, absorbs excess oils, reduces outbreaks, detoxifies the skin, eliminates traces of acne and minor inflammation and helps to retain skin’s hydration. Leaves the skin feeling clean, fresh, revitalized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e \u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​\u003c\/span\u003eRecommended to use twice a week as clarifying treatment for oily, combination skin, skin with enlarged pores, blemishes, acne. Once a week to combat skin dullness, tiredness and occasional inflammation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Kaolin, Glycerin, Montmorillonite, Diatomaceous Earth, Butylene Glycol, Aqua, Sodium PCA, Sodium levulinate, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium anisate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Charcoal Powder, Alchemilla Vulgaris (Lady's Mantle) Extract, Algae (Algae) Extract, Nasturtium Officinale (Watercress) Flower\/Leaf Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 75810 (Chlorophyll), Rhamnose, Maltodextrin, Glucose, Glucuronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e16% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916409999687,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-detox-ultra-purifying-mud-mask-60ml-293845.jpg?v=1739897183"},{"product_id":"madara-peel-creamy-clay-aha-peel-mask-60ml","title":"MÁDARA PEEL Creamy Clay AHA Peel Mask 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eUniting 7% lactic acid and micro-clay, this supercharged face mask works to gently polish the skin’s surface, sloughing off dead skin cells and unclogging pores to reveal a clearer, fresher and more radiant complexion.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eThe dermatologically tested formula encourages a more even skin tone and improves texture, contributing to softer, smoother and brighter skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eEnriched with white clay which binds impurities and helps prevent breakouts, as well as jojoba oil and extract of yarrow that boast soothing and anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eNot suitable for fragile, hypersensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal;\"\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gently massage over clean face and neck in circular motions, avoiding the eye area. Leave on for 3-10 minutes. Follow with a moisturiser of your choice. Use 2-3 times weekly, avoid sun exposure after use. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Kaolin, Lactic Acid, Glycerin, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Potassium Hydroxide, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Aroma, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Palmitic acid, Perlite, Stearic Acid, Achillea Millefolium (Yarrow) Extract, Charcoal Powder, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: ET;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916412555591,"sku":"","price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-peel-creamy-clay-aha-peel-mask-60ml-458560.jpg?v=1739897164"},{"product_id":"madara-his-after-shave-serum-75ml","title":"MÁDARA HIS After Shave Serum 75ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBeat dryness and discomfort with this after shave serum. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe refreshing formula instantly tones and soothes the skin, helping prevent ingrown hair and minimising breakouts and razor bumps. Enriched with skin-identical moisturisers and antioxidant-rich oak bark that hydrate and calm irritated skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean, dry face and neck after shaving.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Glycerin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cantharellus cibarius (chanterelle) extract, Polyglyceryl-6 Stearate, Sodium PCA, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Isoamyl Laurate, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Aqua, Caffeine, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Polyglyceryl-6 Behenate, Aroma, Octyldodecanol, Xanthan Gum, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Cellulose, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Sodium Benzoate, Menthyl Lactate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus Oil, Lavandula Oil\/Extract, Linalyl Acetate, Linalool, Mentha Viridis Leaf Oil, Eugenia Caryophyllus Oil, Carvone, Pinene, Citral, Menthol, Pogostemon Cablin Oil, Camphor, Cinnamomum Cassia Leaf Oil, Laurus Nobilis Leaf Oil, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil, Beta-Caryophyllene, Terpineol, Citronellol, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916432544071,"sku":null,"price":29.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-his-after-shave-serum-75ml-114715.jpg?v=1739897163"},{"product_id":"madara-his-face-cream50ml","title":"MÁDARA HIS Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAchieve instantly energised and hydrated skin with this one-and-done moisturiser. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis lightweight, fast-absorbing moisturiser deeply hydrates and revives dull and tired complexions. Enriched with brightening vitamin C, skin-identical moisturisers, antioxidant-rich oak bark and smoothing chanterelle, it instantly comforts the skin for a soft and supple feel. Targets excess oiliness and improves the look of skin tone. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin every morning and evening.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Aqua, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cantharellus cibarius (chanterelle) extract, Cetearyl Alcohol, Butylene Glycol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Sodium PCA, Potassium Hydroxide, Ferulic Acid, Tocopherol, Sodium Citrate, Aroma, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Xanthan Gum, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Sodium phytate, Citric acid, CI 75815 (Chlorophyllin Copper Complex), Alteromonas Ferment Extract, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Phenethyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Potassium Sorbate, Maltodextrin, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus Oil, Lavandula Oil\/Extract, Linalyl Acetate, Linalool, Mentha Viridis Leaf Oil, Eugenol, Eugenia Caryophyllus Oil, Carvone, Pinene, Citral, Menthol, Pogostemon Cablin Oil, Camphor, Cinnamomum Cassia Leaf Oil, Laurus Nobilis Leaf Oil, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil, Beta-Caryophyllene, Terpineol, Citronellol, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916453024071,"sku":null,"price":39.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-his-face-cream-50ml-860733.jpg?v=1739897177"},{"product_id":"madara-his-eye-cream-17ml","title":"MÁDARA HIS Eye Cream 17ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSay goodbye to tired eyes with this rejuvenating eye cream. Enriched with energising caffeine and smoothing chanterelle, it e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003effectively targets dry eye area, puffiness, wrinkles and dark circles. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eSuitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eApply to clean skin morning and evening.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cantharellus cibarius (chanterelle) extract, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium PCA, Dipalmitoyl hydroxyproline, Caffeine, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Coco- Caprylate, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Xanthan Gum, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Cellulose, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Tocopherol, Aroma, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Potassium Hydroxide, Octyldodecanol, Aqua, Sodium phytate, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Vitis vinifera (grape) Leaf Extract, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium Benzoate, Ginkgo Biloba (Ginkgo) Leaf Extract, Potassium Sorbate, Escin, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus Oil, Lavandula Oil\/Extract, Linalyl Acetate, Linalool, Mentha Viridis Leaf Oil, Eugenol, Eugenia Caryophyllus Oil, Carvone, Pinene, Citral, Menthol, Pogostemon Cablin Oil, Camphor, Cinnamomum Cassia Leaf Oil, Laurus Nobilis Leaf Oil, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil, Beta-Caryophyllene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916473504071,"sku":null,"price":27.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-his-eye-cream-17ml-739727.jpg?v=1739897189"},{"product_id":"madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-50ml","title":"MÁDARA Vitamin C Illuminating Recovery Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e​Treat your skin with this glow-enhancing moisturiser that instantly revives dull and tired complexion, promoting more even skin tone. Formulated with a stabilised form of Vitamin C, a potent antioxidant, used in skincare and dermatology to brighten, improve skin tone and promote a healthy glow, it also helps to prevent hyperpigmentation and dark spots. Hyaluronic acid ensures intense hydration, whilst the seaweed extract boosts the brightening effect, leaving the skin feeling softer and smoother and looking youthfully fresh and beautifully radiant.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply daily on clean skin. Recommended to use daily or as a treatment course 2–3 times a year. Avoid direct sun exposure after the application. Use sunscreen afterwards.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Isoamyl Laurate, Betaine, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Sodium PCA, Aroma, Potassium Hydroxide, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Sodium Citrate, Xanthan Gum, Rubus Chamaemorus (Cloudberry) Fruit Extract, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascophyllum Nodosum (Brown Algae) Extract, Citric acid, CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916523835719,"sku":null,"price":40.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-50ml-305593.jpg?v=1739897158"},{"product_id":"madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Vitamin C Illuminating Recovery Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e​Treat your skin with this glow-enhancing moisturiser that instantly revives dull and tired complexion, promoting more even skin tone. Formulated with a stabilised form of Vitamin C, a potent antioxidant, used in skincare and dermatology to brighten, improve skin tone and promote a healthy glow, it also helps to prevent hyperpigmentation and dark spots. Hyaluronic acid ensures intense hydration, whilst the seaweed extract boosts the brightening effect, leaving the skin feeling softer and smoother and looking youthfully fresh and beautifully radiant.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply daily on clean skin. Recommended to use daily or as a treatment course 2–3 times a year. Avoid direct sun exposure after the application. Use sunscreen afterwards.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Isoamyl Laurate, Betaine, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Sodium PCA, Aroma, Potassium Hydroxide, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Sodium Citrate, Xanthan Gum, Rubus Chamaemorus (Cloudberry) Fruit Extract, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Ascophyllum Nodosum (Brown Algae) Extract, Citric acid, CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916599726407,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-vitamin-c-illuminating-recovery-cream-15ml-419448.jpg?v=1739897174"},{"product_id":"madara-vitamin-c-intense-glow-concentrate-30ml","title":"MÁDARA Vitamin C Intense Glow Concentrate 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDial up your skin’s glow with this super-potent brightening concentrate, starring a powerful blend of ferulic acid and vitamins C+E that tackle visible signs of aging such as fine lines, hyperpigmentation and loss of elasticity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFerulic acid works to firm the skin and multiplies its defence against free radical damage, while the combination of vitamins C and E help brighten and even out skin tone, boosting radiance and supporting collagen synthesis.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean skin, follow with a moisturiser. Recommended to use daily or or as a treatment course 2–3 times a year. Avoid direct sun exposure after application and wear sunscreen.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Butylene Glycol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Betaine, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Ferulic Acid, Sodium PCA, Tocopherol, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Oil, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Triheptanoin, Potassium Hydroxide, Cellulose, Aroma, Sodium Citrate, Xanthan Gum, Rubus Chamaemorus (Cloudberry) Fruit Extract, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium phytate, Citric acid, Limonene, Citronellol, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916611522887,"sku":null,"price":42.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-vitamin-c-intense-glow-concentrate-30ml-695517.jpg?v=1739897190"},{"product_id":"blokzeep-shampoo-bar-cornflower-60g","title":"Blokzeep Shampoo Bar Cornflower 60g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDue to the natural ingredients, the Cornflower shampoo bar is suitable for every hair type - and especially for men due to the heavier \u0026amp; fresh scent. Linden blossom extract has been added to this shampoo bar, which has a soothing effect on your scalp. It also helps renew and hydrate damaged skin, which also strengthens your hair roots. The result? A full head of healthy hair!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Cornflower shampoo bar is sustainable for three reasons: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLess water: A normal bottle of shampoo contains 80% water, which must be transported every time. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMore efficient use: A shampoo block lasts 3 times as long as a normal bottle of shampoo. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlastic-free packaging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis Shampoo bar Cornflower is handmade within Europe and transported to the Netherlands in a CO2 neutral manner. Packaging is 100% plastic-free.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eSodium Coco-Sulfate, Aqua, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tilia Cordata Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Limonene, Coumarin, Alpha Isomethyl Ionone, Benzyl Benzoate, Geraniol, CI 42090\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e handmade\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Blokzeep","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50938736804167,"sku":null,"price":8.99,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/blokzeep-shampoo-bar-cornflower-60g-835077.jpg?v=1739897179"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-naokreem-meestele-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Face Cream for Men 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFace cream For Men contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which anti-aging and deep moisturizing effect has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAstaxanthin acts as if on the skin natural doping. This powerful antioxidant can penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. The humidity level balances and premature wrinkles generation decreases. The skin is protected from the attack of UV rays and free radicals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream is well suited for after-shave care.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Age Defence Face Cream for Men:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep moisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti-aging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dryness and scar tissue.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for after-shave care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith light absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran, astaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom the Amazon rainforest \u003ci\u003ecacay\u003c\/i\u003e– oil improves skin elasticity and evens skin tone. Aloe soothes and relieves irritations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, ), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Glycerin**, Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042419835207,"sku":null,"price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-30ml-969154.png?v=1739897169"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Face Cream for Men REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFace cream For Men contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which anti-aging and deep moisturizing effect has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAstaxanthin acts as if on the skin natural doping. This powerful antioxidant can penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. The humidity level balances and premature wrinkles generation decreases. The skin is protected from the attack of UV rays and free radicals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream is well suited for after-shave care.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Age Defence Face Cream for Men:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep moisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti-aging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dryness and scar tissue.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for after-shave care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith light absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran, astaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom the Amazon rainforest \u003ci\u003ecacay\u003c\/i\u003e– oil improves skin elasticity and evens skin tone. Aloe soothes and relieves irritations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, ), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Glycerin**, Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084323389767,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml-844196.png?v=1739979950"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Lemongrass Green 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Unisex deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and keeps you fresh and dry all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe unisex deodorant allows the skin to function naturally and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, sage extract combats odor-causing bacteria, and aloe moisturizes and soothes delicate underarm skin. The deodorant dries quickly and does not leave stains on clothes. The fresh blend of essential oils is suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Unisex deodorant is certified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, so you can be sure you’re using a product that’s not only good for you but also for our planet. Additionally, it is aluminum-free, alcohol-free, and soda-free, and 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh scent that is suitable for both men and women \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia Fruit (Bergamot) Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Limonene, Citral, Linalool, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138263904583,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml-1178078.png?v=1756222794"},{"product_id":"nurme-mint-rosemary-shampoo-for-men-250ml","title":"NURME Mint Rosemary Shampoo for Men 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural shampoo for men contains essential oils of\u003cspan\u003e mint\u003c\/span\u003e and rosemary, which have a refreshing and revitalizing effect on hair. The shampoo leaves a pleasant fragrance and invigorates hair roots.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRosemary essential oil helps to soothe dry scalp problems, while peppermint revitalizes and refreshes. This natural shampoo for men has been rated by users as one of the best hair cleansers to fight dandruff. Stress, the changing seasons and a weakened immune system are just a few of the factors that can cover the scalp with white patches of dandruff. Rosemary soothes itchy scalps and contains anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial components, so in milder cases, the right choice of shampoo may be all you need to get rid of dandruff.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMassage a small amount of shampoo into the hair in a circular motion. Leave on for 1-2 minutes and rinse. Repeat the process if necessary and use a conditioner.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Oil, Citric Acid, Glyceryl Oleate, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene*\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e*Occurs naturally in essential oil\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52880600006983,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mint-rosemary-shampoo-for-men-250ml-8660282.webp?v=1765078814"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-rich-hydra-barrier-cica-cream-40ml","title":"MÁDARA SOS Rich Hydra-Barrier CICA Cream 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eInstantly sooth and comfort very dry, dehydrated, stressed and reactive skin with this rich hydra-barrier cream. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with the hydrating and calming Centella Asiatica (CICA) extract to bolster skin’s protective barrier and help restore the epidermal balance. Hyaluronic acid, soothing bisabolol, nurturing shea butter and repairing ceramides in the formulation help to improve moisture retention, prevent dryness-induced discomfort and signs of premature ageing. Works to diminish the feeling of taut and itchy skin and unveils a better-looking complexion by promoting skin’s healthy radiance.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a generous amount to clean skin. Use in the morning and night or whenever your skin feels dry, taut and stressed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e ALOE BARBADENSIS (ALOE) LEAF JUICE*; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL*; GLYCERIN; THEOBROMA CACAO (COCOA) SEED BUTTER*; CETEARYL ALCOHOL; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; POLYGLYCERYL-3 STEARATE; BETAINE; SODIUM PCA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE; ISOAMYL LAURATE; OCTYLDODECANOL; AROMA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; AQUA; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; XANTHAN GUM; BISABOLOL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; PAEONIA LACTIFLORA (PEONY) ROOT EXTRACT; BORAGO OFFICINALIS (BORAGE) SEED OIL*; CELLULOSE; GLYCOSPHINGOLIPIDS; LACTIC ACID; OENOTHERA BIENNIS (EVENING PRIMROSE) OIL*; RUBUS IDAEUS (RASPBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; SODIUM PHYTATE; CENTELLA ASIATICA (PENNYWORT) LEAF EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; TOCOPHEROL; HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID; SODIUM HYALURONATE; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***; CITRONELLOL**; GERANIOL**; BENZYL SALICYLATE**; EUGENOL**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e27% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52919609229639,"sku":null,"price":37.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-rich-hydra-barrier-cica-cream-40ml-2135696.jpg?v=1765327460"},{"product_id":"madara-cleansing-milk-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Cleansing Milk 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCleanse the skin and remove makeup with this mild and soothing cleansing milk. Formulated with an innovative complex of 100% natural oils that facilitate the makeup removal and provide a super-smooth skin feel. Gently, yet effectively removes even waterproof makeup, leaving the skin smooth, fresh and hydrated. Boosts the performance of subsequently used moisturisers. The non-irritating velvety formula is also suitable for use around the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount on a cotton pad to remove makeup and cleanse the skin from all impurities. Rinse off with water or wipe off with a clean cotton pad or a cloth. Follow with a moisturiser.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e ALOE BARBADENSIS (ALOE) LEAF JUICE*; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL*; SUCROSE DISTEARATE; PENTYLENE GLYCOL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; ISOAMYL LAURATE; SUCROSE STEARATE; GLYCERIN**; AROMA; PALMITIC ACID; STEARIC ACID; XANTHAN GUM; LACTIC ACID; GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE; AVENA SATIVA (OAT) KERNEL EXTRACT*; CALENDULA OFFICINALIS (CALENDULA) FLOWER EXTRACT*; PLANTAGO MAJOR (PLANTAIN) LEAF EXTRACT*; TILIA CORDATA (LINDEN) FLOWER EXTRACT*; AQUA; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; SODIUM PHYTATE; TOCOPHEROL; VANILLIN; JASMINUM OFFICINALE (JASMINE) EXTRACT; LEUCONOSTOC\/RADISH ROOT FERMENT FILTRATE; BENZYL SALICYLATE***; LIMONENE***; CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL; CITRAL***; CITRONELLOL***; GERANIOL***; EUGENOL***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e25% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53351758397767,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-cleansing-milk-200ml-1698263.jpg?v=1771463649"},{"product_id":"madara-melting-cleansing-oil-100ml","title":"MÁDARA Melting Cleansing Oil 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis oil-based cleanser with nourishing lipids deeply, yet delicately purifies and cleans the skin, melting away long wear makeup and mineral sunscreen. Removes impurities without irritating the skin or stripping its natural protective barrier. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe oil melts upon contact with water and is easy to rinse. Leaves the skin clean, luxuriously soft and nourished. Suitable for use around the eyes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMassage the oil into dry or damp skin, add some water.  Rinse off and follow with your regular face cleansing routine. Suitable for double cleansing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; GLYCERIN**; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL*; AQUA; SUCROSE LAURATE; SUCROSE PALMITATE; AROMA; ALCOHOL; TOCOPHEROL; CI 77163 (BISMUTH CHLORIDE OXIDE)****; OENOTHERA BIENNIS (EVENING PRIMROSE) OIL*; PRUNUS AMYGDALUS DULCIS (ALMOND) OIL*; GLYCOSPHINGOLIPIDS; GLYCOLIPIDS; BENZYL SALICYLATE**; LIMONENE**; CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL; CITRAL**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e****Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e39% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53351769407815,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-melting-cleansing-oil-100ml-3502637.jpg?v=1771463660"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/for-men.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}